## Core capabilities

- **Architecture:** cloud-native systems, edge computing, event-driven design
- **Machine learning:** model lifecycle, ONNX optimizations, on-device inference
- **IoT & connectivity:** LoRaWAN, MQTT, device provisioning and fleet management
- **Observability & ops:** metrics, tracing, alerting, HA data stores
- **Security & compliance:** secure device onboarding, least-privilege access, data privacy

